    <td class="rowodd" valign="top"><i><a href="/account/profile.php?user_id=17391">Paul Contreras</a></i></td>
    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">Cured the glitch that the centering is not centering when the end of the file is not as far as the bottom of the window.&nbsp;&nbsp;Added a couple of new modes, these act just like zt and zb in normal mode. They are shift-ESC and shift-F1 respectively.&nbsp;&nbsp;So now you've got all zz, zt & zb as smooth-equivalents: ESC, S-ESC and S-F1 respectively.</td>
</tr>
